Package searchengine

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileLoader
    A class that reads in the file and adds the text as pages on a list of all pages.
    InvertedIndex
    This class creates an InvertedIndex object.
    Page
    A class that creates a Page opbject from the list of pages and defines a score for every page
    PageRanker
    A class responsible for assigning all pages that will be shown in the search engine a score, which they are subsequently sorted by.
    QueryHandler
    Handles a complex query and searches through an invertedIndex and creates a result of response pages.
    Response
    A class that contains one method for sending a response to the webserver.
    WebServer
    A class that handles all the information retrieved from and sent to the webserver in order to run the search engine.
